metadata.name: Relationships
metadata.description:
Relationships begin when people meet together: family, lovers, friends, or past people.  It may be just a short time, or it may be a long period of time.  But when it comes to spending time together, there are many stories.  in memory, whether it is a good story  or a bad story  It will settle in us forever.


Color : Blue Red
Size : 5,000x6,000
July 2022
